00:18:34,483 --> 00:18:36,650
So we studied fusion control
in the New England grid

331
00:18:36,650 --> 00:18:39,770
in greater detail using a GenX
model of the ISO New England

332
00:18:39,770 --> 00:18:43,560
grid and reservoir hydro
