T in the plasma,

815
00:42:46,290 --> 00:42:49,010
you can capture that neutron in
a lithium-containing material

816
00:42:49,010 --> 00:42:50,190
and breed tritium.

817
00:42:50,190 --> 00:42:51,870
So it's straightforward
in principle,

818
00:42:51,870 --> 00:42:53,810
