822
00:43:01,730 --> 00:43:04,820
at any given point in
the plant's lifetime,

823
00:43:04,820 --> 00:43:06,860
how to extract that
tritium efficiently

824
00:43:06,860 --> 00:43:09,410
and get it ready and
prepared for fueling.

825
00:43:09,410 --> 00:43:13,100
