833
00:43:25,470 --> 00:43:28,250
with understanding how to
breed the tritium using fusion

834
00:43:28,250 --> 00:43:31,880
neutrons in the
lithium-containing materials.

835
00:43:31,880 --> 00:43:34,010
We have a major
experimental campaign here

836
00:43:34,010 --> 00:43:35,810
at the MIT Plasma
