848
00:44:03,200 --> 00:44:04,880
to from the fission sector.

849
00:44:04,880 --> 00:44:08,060
So we have to do a lot of work
to develop advanced materials

850
00:44:08,060 --> 00:44:09,890
and maintenance
strategies that are going

851
00:44:09,890 --> 00:44:12,030
